    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plot.</h2>You work in a small laboratory for water research, enjoying a quiet and peaceful life you have with your wife and son.<br><br><br>Everything changes when Refleaktion Corporation becomes its new owner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/fe3c3dc70b43d9bd4ca4e7bf207a78c5.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/fe3c3dc70b43d9bd4ca4e7bf207a78c5.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/fe3c3dc70b43d9bd4ca4e7bf207a78c5.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Having to make decisions that go against your morality, you keep telling yourself your lifelong project will result in a discovery that does more good than harm.<br><br>But there is a limit to everything.<br><br>Soon you find out that the next step in your research is conducting experiments on people. You quit your job in order to escape to the countryside with your family and clear yourself of suspicion. <br><br>Except when you return home your wife and son are missing, and there is a corpse of an unknown man hanging from a ceiling in your study.<br><br>Get ready for it is just the beginning.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/ea3d544fbefa9f406acbc2596e99b279.avif?t=1699449698\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in the world of Leak, where science meets rituals. Feel the fine line between hope and despair. Live out the story of a man who does the unthinkable in hopes to return to his normal life. <br><br>Resist the spirits that have entered our world in the form of pure agony and nightmares.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/75f7560a9c9cdc6bd48f2898cb3ef484.avif?t=1699449698\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Legends.</h2>Collect lost pages from the book – it will help you learn more about all that is happening.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/1987d6197159c6f948e9e83c8d1ad2d7.avif?t=1699449698\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Locations.</h2>Explore the house and the surrounding area – much of the action will take place outside the house.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/9e3822fda182d40224a34e4070c7624f.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/9e3822fda182d40224a34e4070c7624f.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/9e3822fda182d40224a34e4070c7624f.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Do not hesitate to wander around – you can find a lot of interesting and mysterious things. Do not go too far into the forest however or you are risking freezing to death!<br><br>As you progress through the game, you will transition to other locations and explore memories of the main character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/be9152d877ee5a28236c3b6421421bb1.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/be9152d877ee5a28236c3b6421421bb1.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/be9152d877ee5a28236c3b6421421bb1.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay.</h2><br>Examine the items you find – you will be able to interact with some of them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/1d10f5d2e662fed6f38fb328de0eb0b7.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/1d10f5d2e662fed6f38fb328de0eb0b7.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/1d10f5d2e662fed6f38fb328de0eb0b7.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be careful while exploring and never stop moving – they are always near.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b52049645589c6f7aa55cd299c976486.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b52049645589c6f7aa55cd299c976486.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b52049645589c6f7aa55cd299c976486.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Breaking the fourth wall! We included interactions between the main character and your real life. Be careful. <br><br>Do not answer your phone or check your email.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b9faad614dbbf17918a4bd0a39464166.poster.avif?t=1699449698\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b9faad614dbbf17918a4bd0a39464166.webm?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183890/extras/b9faad614dbbf17918a4bd0a39464166.mp4?t=1699449698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sound Design.</h2>Music and sound design will make you feel to the max the horror, desperation, and grief of the main character – even by just listening to the game OST separately.<br><br><br>Be the first to get the latest news! Links to our social media can be found on our website. There we share news about the game development process and exciting new materials. <br><br>We look forward to you joining our community!",
